TY  - JOUR
T1  - Some Heuristics for Scheduling Jobs on Parallel Machines with Setups
AU  - So, Kut C.
Y1  - 1990/04/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.36.4.467
