N2  - The full covariance probit model is highly regarded due to the flexibility with which it can represent cross brand effects. Explicit formulae for these cross brand effects for the general N brand case have never appeared in print, nor have the direct elasticities for the model. This note fills that omission.
AB  - The full covariance probit model is highly regarded due to the flexibility with which it can represent cross brand effects. Explicit formulae for these cross brand effects for the general N brand case have never appeared in print, nor have the direct elasticities for the model. This note fills that omission.
